column2: SELECT u.AGCNr, u.RAdeg_OC, u.DECdeg_OC, u.Dist_Mpc, u.z as hi_z, n.objid, n.distance, n.type, n.mode, o.ra as ra_near, o.dec as dec_near, o.u, o.g, o.r, o.i, o.z, o.specObjID, z.z as photo_z, z.zErr as photo_zErr into mydb.environment_# FROM mydb.udg1#_newinfo as u    outer apply dbo.fGetNearbyObjAllEq(u.RAdeg_OC, u.DECdeg_OC, #) as n    left join GALAXY as o on n.objid = o.objid        join Photoz as z on n.objid = z.objid
